<h4>The map markers</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
The two animated markers on the corridor map: the walking crew figure
(#R34967(AnimateCrewA), a two-frame walk cycle) and the blinking room cursor
(#R35016(AnimateCrewB), four shrinking boxes). All are 24&times;12-pixel
XOR-blit sprites.
</div>
