<h4>The air ducts</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
The duct overlay drawn as the view background when the viewed position is
inside the crawlways — one map per deck, at #R25716(DuctMapUpper),
#R25835(DuctMapMiddle) and #R25996(DuctMapLower).
</div>
