<h4>The Narcissus</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
The escape shuttle's cabin, stored run-length-encoded at
#R30720(NarcissusLayout) and expanded at draw time by
#R33644(NarcissusBackground), with each cell coloured by its
#R30861(NarcissusAttrs) byte.
</div>
