<h4>The title screen</h4>
<div class="paragraph">
The ALIEN egg picture composed by #R42581(DrawIntroScreen) from the tile map
at #R40504(IntroTileMap) over #R62000(TileBitmaps), with the lower rows
coloured by #R40669(IntroAttributes) — the green is the egg's glow.
</div>
